# UnrealMCP plugin — keep the publishable surface clean.
# (Source/, Config/, Python/*.py, *.sh, pyproject.toml, the .uplugin and CHANGELOG ship;
#  everything below is a build/runtime artifact that must not be packaged.)

# Unreal build output
Binaries/
Intermediate/
Saved/
DerivedDataCache/

# Python sidecar artifacts
Python/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.egg-info/

# Runtime logs
*.log
